{{notability|Biographies|date=October 2013}}
'''Gregory L. Charvat''' is author of ''Small and Short-Range Radar Systems'', Co-Founder of Butterfly Network Inc, and advisor to the [http://cameraculture.media.mit.edu Camera Culture Group] at Massachusetts Institute of Technology [[MIT Media Lab]].

== Career ==

Charvat is best known for his through-wall [[radar]] imaging system<ref name="E.FinnMITnews">{{cite web | last =Finn | first =Emily | title =Seeing through walls | work =MIT news | publisher =Massachusetts Institute of Technology | date =2011-10-18 | url = http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2011/ll-seeing-through-walls-1018.html | accessdate = 2013-10-23}}</ref><ref>Additional references regarding the Through-Wall Radar Imaging system:
