ay-final-ratings-july-26-2016/|title=Tuesday final ratings: ‘AGT’ and ‘Bachelorette’ adjust up, ‘Zoo,’ ‘Coupled’ and ‘Whose Line’ adjust down|last=Porter|first=Rick|work=[[TV by the Numbers]]|date=July 27, 2016|accessdate=July 27, 2016}}</ref> | ShortSummary = Gordon meets a woman who works countless hours to keep her hotel and events business afloat. After assessing the situation, he urges her son to learn the business and take the reins from his mother. Together, they throw a fairytale wedding at the castle. | LineColor = 000 }} }}
